# Workspace runtime data
# L1 system prompts (AGENTS/SOUL/TOOLS/IDENTITY/HEARTBEAT) are git-tracked and force-updated.
# L2/L3 runtime files are gitignored — initialized from .example templates at startup.
workspace/.ResearchClaw/USER.md
workspace/.ResearchClaw/BOOTSTRAP.md
workspace/.ResearchClaw/BOOTSTRAP.md.done
workspace/.ResearchClaw/*_backup_*.md
workspace/MEMORY.md
workspace/USER.md
workspace/.openclaw/
